  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Speed of Light
Formula: c = 299,792,458 m/s in vacuum
Note:    Foundation of special relativity; universal speed limit

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Photosynthesis
Formula: 6CO₂+6H₂O+light→C₆H₁₂O₆+6O₂
Note:    How plants produce energy from sunlight

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   DNA Structure
Formula: Double helix; A-T and G-C base pairs
Note:    Stores and transmits genetic information

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   pH Definition
Formula: pH = -log[H+]
Note:    Measure of hydrogen ion concentration; 7 is neutral

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Planck's Constant
Formula: h = 6.626×10⁻³⁴ J·s
Note:    Quantum of action; E = hf for photon energy

